{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "customer_service", "channel": "customer_feedback", "user": "david.thompson", "message": "Team, we've seen an uptick in online orders over the past week. Let's make sure to continue offering excellent customer service as we handle these orders. Thanks!", "created_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "in_store_experience", "channel": "recipe_cards", "user": "jane_doe", "message": "We've received positive feedback on the store layout changes. Let's continue to find ways to improve customer experience in our stores.", "created_at": 1620501000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "customer_service", "channel": "customer_feedback", "user": "john_smith", "message": "I've been getting a lot of positive feedback about our delivery services. It seems like our system upgrades are really making a difference.", "created_at": 1620502000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "in_store_experience", "channel": "recipe_cards", "user": "jane_doe", "message": "Just a reminder about the team meeting this Friday. We'll be discussing updates to our in-store promotional displays.", "created_at": 1620503000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "customer_service", "channel": "customer_feedback", "user": "david.thompson", "message": "Let's have a meeting next week to discuss the feedback from our customer satisfaction survey. I'll send out a calendar invite by the end of this week.", "created_at": 1620504000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "in_store_experience", "channel": "recipe_cards", "user": "jane_doe", "message": "Team, as of February 25, 2024, we've started a new initiative to provide recipe cards in our stores. We've been printing over 200 recipe cards monthly and distributing them across all Lee's Market stores. The initial feedback has been positive, and we plan to continue this moving forward.", "create_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "in_store_experience", "channel": "recipe_cards", "user": "david.thompson", "message": "That's great news, Jane! I believe this initiative will enhance our customers' in-store experience and facilitate their shopping journey. Let's keep an eye on customer feedback regarding the recipe cards to ensure we're meeting their needs.", "create_at": 1620500100000}}
